# [https://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html](i3wm)

## Setup

### Adding i3 to the autostart

Now open the xfce settings manager and go to session and startup.
Switch to the Application Autostart tab and add a new Application.

### Disable the existing window manager and desktop from xfce

Now you have to change the restart style of 3 items. xfwm4,
xfdesktop and xfce4-panel needed "Never" as restart style.
After that you can quit everyone of them, just click "Quit Program"
for xfce4-panel, xfdesktop and xfwm4.
